  <brief_title>Pharmacological Study That Measures Omeprazole Effect on Aspirins Absorption in Healthy Volunteers</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Proton Pump Inhibitor (Omeprazole) on Acetosalisylic Acid Absorption.</official_title>
